front.title: •••Womp Rat
front.gametext: * Ferocity = destiny. Habitat: exterior planet sites. Ferocity +1 for each other womp rat at same site. Lost if 'bullseyed' by Luke's T-16 Skyhopper present.
front.lore: Carnivorous rodents. Typically found in Beggar's Canyon. About the size of an average thermal exhaust port.
